@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}

note over App, VFS
<b>普通文件系统 open() 完整流程</b>
- inode: 文件本体
- dentry: 文件名->inode 映射
- file: 进程打开的文件实例
- fd: 文件描述符(进程私有)
end note

box "【用户态 User Space】" #LightYellow
actor App
end box

box "【内核态 Kernel Space】" #LightCyan
participant "VFS 虚拟文件系统" as VFS
participant "super_block" as SB
participant "dentry cache" as Dentry
participant "inode manager" as Inode
participant "file struct" as File
end box

database "Disk" as Disk

App -> VFS: <color:red>①</color> open("/home/test.txt", O_RDONLY)
activate VFS

VFS -> VFS: <color:red>②</color> 路径拆分解析
note right: / -> home -> test.txt

VFS -> Dentry: <color:red>③</color> 查找 dentry (dcache)
activate Dentry
Dentry --> VFS: 返回目标 dentry
deactivate Dentry

VFS -> Inode: <color:red>④</color> 通过 dentry 获取 inode
activate Inode
Inode -> SB: 读取文件系统信息
SB --> Inode: 返回 inode 操作集
Inode --> VFS: 返回有效 inode
deactivate Inode

VFS -> File: <color:red>⑤</color> 分配 struct file
activate File
note right: 绑定 dentry, inode, f_pos=0
File --> VFS: 返回 file 对象
deactivate File

VFS -> VFS: <color:red>⑥</color> 分配文件描述符 fd
VFS --> App: <color:red>⑦</color> 返回 fd
deactivate VFS
@enduml